{"tid":1582662,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵：預計財產損失三至四千萬 或需成立港鐵保安隊","createTime":"2019-09-20T08:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T11:59:21.000Z","uid":100535,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e47ff5e18af47fe4364d430e8d8000cefbfdef10","tid":1582662,"uid":100535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T08:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uAC5kWh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuAC5kWh.jpg&h=7993cbb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港鐵主席歐陽伯權接受彭博訪問時稱，反修例活動導致香港地鐵乘客數量下降，使用港鐵系統的乘客正在呈下降趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n歐陽伯權又表示，財產損失在3000萬至4000萬元之間。<br />\n<br />\n歐陽伯權又指，對港鐵成為目標感到驚訝，表示「這就像經歷了一場動盪」。他又指，可能是因為在許多最激烈的抗議活動發生時，愈來愈多的人選擇周末留在家中。<br />\n對於穆迪和惠譽均因動盪而調整對香港的看法，進而調低港鐵的評級展望。歐陽伯權說，「在財務方面，港鐵公司是一家非常穩固的公司」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，大公報亦報道，歐陽伯權指，若暴力衝擊一直升級，港鐵「無防暴裝備，無地鐵防暴隊，只有一樣，就系關閘」，長遠或需成立港鐵自己的保安隊伍。"},{"pid":"2104820ee13f9ee62f28dc1d39fd18f129f58b81","tid":1582662,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"[公海 文宣整合] 9.29全球反極權集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581746</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8kyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=56cb6e2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8kyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=631f2348\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"309de6cd3b5946e106e211b15f0fc52f6ddd27f6","tid":1582662,"uid":33930,"like":0,"